{"tid":1964321,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都好想死","createTime":"2020-04-08T17:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T10:47:40.000Z","uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc2c74d2ffdb6e9b1468d0ab4dfbfc6c3834942","tid":1964321,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"幾時可以"},{"pid":"d1cd424de7e58eed6722ca69bc5fba60d5590f49","tid":1964321,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"死啦"},{"pid":"2b6df8da4531552437e1d2ab0521cb30278f5621","tid":1964321,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1cd424de7e58eed6722ca69bc5fba60d5590f49","tid":1964321,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"死啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"幫我"},{"pid":"dcb1395877adf4e0066e6216f3e59de9f95f3c66","tid":1964321,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:00:13.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0c61bc94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n諸事不順皆因不孝，諸事不順皆因犯邪淫<br />\n<br />\n只要犯以上兩種，你既運氣，人生，福報就會不斷下降，這是千真萬確既事實<br />\n想要人生變得更好，第一孝順，第二戒邪淫，（包括打丁，叫雞，一夜情等等），第三行善積德<br />\n只要照住上面３樣去做好一年，你會慢慢發覺自己既人生越黎越好。<br />\n<br />\n可睇秦東魁老師講既ＹＯＵＴＵＢＥ視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=40b87f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA</a>"},{"pid":"ff8b334897cff097413f32275422817fe1d392da","tid":1964321,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"爽死"},{"pid":"a9c8c204d9ec7b2d010262929305f9ec5e25a60a","tid":1964321,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:31:10.000Z","msg":"每朝起身都好辛苦 無人明"},{"pid":"9e82240d8e7b2d51aa724a0b0d596e64991f93b2","tid":1964321,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f0c80f1e7df3708b25df54915f2053c02f1b5d4","tid":1964321,"uid":273587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T18:51:17.000Z","msg":"我都有哩種感覺<br />\n生存到宜加都係因為屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得要白頭人送黑頭人好不孝"},{"pid":"134b3c26cc4fe665fa41a0cea86252aad5abe04e","tid":1964321,"uid":192607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"有咩搞到咁想死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbf35b05941e1e81e4b5d74f97a5459602d6b6b","tid":1964321,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"134b3c26cc4fe665fa41a0cea86252aad5abe04e","tid":1964321,"uid":192607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"有咩搞到咁想死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T19:14:43.000Z","msg":"使唔使考埋牌先可以想死？"},{"pid":"06e7f3ba876f61f8cce20880ba96bb351098ab1b","tid":1964321,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc2c74d2ffdb6e9b1468d0ab4dfbfc6c3834942","tid":1964321,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"幾時可以"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"&quot;或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=55bc2891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"}]}